{"id":604518,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/01/乡闲-染香故事/","date":"2019-01-24T19:03:59Z","modified":"2019-01-24T19:16:58Z","title":"乡闲 | 染香故事","content":"<p>作者：wentommy   来源：乡闲</p>\n<p>2018年5月22日，久违了广大正能量网友的袁小靓小姐的这条微博，引发了热议。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604522\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/1-36.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"622\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/1-36.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/1-36-241x300.jpg 241w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/1-36-768x956.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/1-36-823x1024.jpg 823w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<div class=\"text_exposed_show\">\n<p>想当年靓姨也是军中正能量偶像、青年团指定爱国学习标兵、环球时报牌民族主义火炬手兼著名毛派教育家庆东教授密友……</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604523\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/2-38.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"954\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/2-38.jpg 1050w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/2-38-157x300.jpg 157w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/2-38-768x1466.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/2-38-537x1024.jpg 537w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>以前喊人家小甜甜，现在是loser们</em></p>\n<p>如今……情何以堪，何以堪啊。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604525\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/3-37.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"497\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/3-37.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/3-37-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/3-37-300x298.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/3-37-70x70.jpg 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/3-37-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>粉笔张小龙吐槽教育现状</em></p>\n<p>网友 @labele 感慨：染香孩子填个表就上学，扭头骂loser，（粉笔）张小龙缴税千万担心孩子上不了学，现在被抓汉奸批斗，太魔幻现实了。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604526\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/4-36.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"565\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/4-36.jpg 1010w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/4-36-266x300.jpg 266w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/4-36-768x868.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/4-36-906x1024.jpg 906w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>@染香 这个微博营销账号，一度把民间盛赞的正能量女神袁小靓推在前台，与庆东、马南、法天、点爷等有一搭没一搭地合作，花样传播正能量。</p>\n<p>正所谓：花红柳绿，千杯不醉；男女搭配，干活不累。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604527\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/5-33.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"351\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/5-33.jpg 800w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/5-33-300x211.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/5-33-768x540.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><em>中间的女子就是染香ID之出镜者袁小靓</em></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604529\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/6-27.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"604\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/6-27.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/6-27-248x300.jpg 248w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><em>庆东教授与染香女士举杯庆祝某起钓鱼事件的圆满成功</em></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604530\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/7-25.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"233\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/7-25.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/7-25-300x140.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>庆东教授蜜汁自豪</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right\">延伸阅读</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right\">庆东教授二三事</p>\n<p>拿染香打艳镲，是庆东教授乐此不疲的小把戏。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604531\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/8-24.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"639\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/8-24.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/8-24-235x300.jpg 235w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><em>弘扬乳家文化</em></p>\n<p>在男人堆里活色生香，小靓、小靓，还故意放纵了同侪男士们的成人话题、带色儿玩笑，染香也因此成为正能量团建活动的最佳搭档，天南地北各种政商埋单的红色“名人行”，游山玩水打秋风的雅事，仿若“无川不成军”， 一度非靓不成行。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604532\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/9-19.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"624\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/9-19.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/9-19-240x300.jpg 240w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/9-19-768x959.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/9-19-820x1024.jpg 820w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>三微名人行</em></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604533\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/10-15.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/10-15.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/10-15-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/10-15-768x576.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/10-15-1024x768.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604534\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/11-18.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"665\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/11-18.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/11-18-225x300.jpg 225w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/11-18-768x1022.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/11-18-770x1024.jpg 770w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>红色龙岩行</em></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604535\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/12-14.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"667\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/12-14.jpg 960w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/12-14-225x300.jpg 225w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/12-14-768x1024.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604536\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/13-13.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/13-13.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/13-13-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><em>环球时报南疆行</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right\">延伸阅读</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right\">点子正与他的战友们</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604537\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/14-7.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"667\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/14-7.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/14-7-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><em>与南子同框</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right\">延伸阅读</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right\">司马南合影哲学考</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604538\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/15-10.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"648\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/15-10.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/15-10-232x300.jpg 232w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/15-10-768x995.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/15-10-791x1024.jpg 791w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><em>崇左名人行</em></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604539\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/16-8.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"688\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/16-8.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/16-8-218x300.jpg 218w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/16-8-768x1057.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/16-8-744x1024.jpg 744w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><em>打公知——正能量名博烟台行</em></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604540\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/17-6.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"713\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/17-6.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/17-6-210x300.jpg 210w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/17-6-768x1095.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/17-6-718x1024.jpg 718w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><em>继续瞄准公知——名博渤海老区行</em></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604541\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/18-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/18-4.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/18-4-273x300.jpg 273w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/18-4-768x844.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/18-4-932x1024.jpg 932w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><em>体育总局大V行</em></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604542\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/19-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"469\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/19-3.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/19-3-300x281.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/19-3-768x720.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/19-3-1024x960.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><em>正能量秋风团</em></p>\n<p>一眼望去，多次与染香携游的点子正、袁国宝、侯宁、石述思、传媒老王……还真是这国正能量商业公关文化的基本盘。</p>\n<p>比如大约8点20分发的伊利国乳站台事件。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right\">延伸阅读</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right\">在潘董带领下的自媒体大V们</p>\n<p>正能量秋风团里出勤率最高的，大概是自干五大统领点子正先生，小靓与国宝，并列亚军，也算得袁门双杰了。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604543\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/20-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"878\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/20-3.jpg 1050w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/20-3-171x300.jpg 171w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/20-3-768x1348.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/20-3-583x1024.jpg 583w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>网络名人走进张家口，其中的重要活动就包括这个“新媒体舆论引导战略研讨会”。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604544\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/21-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/21-3.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/21-3-300x169.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/21-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/21-3-1024x576.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>中间的白领是袁小靓女士，傍边的眼镜就是新媒体舆情巨师袁国宝先生</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604545\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/22-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"335\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/22-2.jpg 720w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/22-2-300x201.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/22-2-360x240.jpg 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>当袁小靓定居美国，秀她在当地电影院看完战狼II后的热泪盈眶时，那些延请她担任红色旅游贵宾的革命老区红区领导们，怕是看着手里积攒的餐饮游乐发票，欲哭无泪了。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604546\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/23-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"1495\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/23-1.jpg 1050w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/23-1-100x300.jpg 100w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/23-1-768x2297.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/23-1-342x1024.jpg 342w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>女孩的心思，您别猜？</p>\n<p>鄙人倒觉得，像染香这类网络时代的情绪引导师，看似多变随机，其实深谋远虑，有路径可循。</p>\n<p>这冷不丁蹦出来的一句：中华人民共和国日本省，显然是要收割U型锁爱好者们的喝彩与崇拜。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604548\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/24-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"682\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/24-1.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/24-1-220x300.jpg 220w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/24-1-768x1048.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/24-1-750x1024.jpg 750w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>日本省</em></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604549\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/25-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"574\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/25-1.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/25-1-261x300.jpg 261w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>走进八一</em></p>\n<p>解放军小伙子，你们的靓姨来了！</p>\n<p>红军小伙子对袁小靓的青睐，怕是媲美了蓝军少男对邓丽君的期待。何日君再来？佳人已不在。</p>\n<p>靓姨来了，又坐飞机漂洋过海。</p>\n<p>很可能会后悔：再坐飞机归来。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">▼▼▼</p>\n<p>袁小靓之“五转公”，湖北随州杨氏恒均先生堪称领路人。</p>\n<p>2014年12月11日，在加拿大联邦政府注册的国际新媒体合作组织(International New Media Cooperation Organization )在北京宣布成立，杨担任了创会主席。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604550\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/26-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"663\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/26-1.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/26-1-226x300.jpg 226w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/26-1-768x1019.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/26-1-772x1024.jpg 772w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604551\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/27-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"666\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/27-1.jpg 460w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/27-1-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>杨先生与前生活秘书袁小姐合影</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604552\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/28.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"650\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/28.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/28-231x300.jpg 231w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/28-768x998.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/28-788x1024.jpg 788w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>老杨头护花</em></p>\n<p>杨先生何许人也？</p>\n<p>其线上线下言论与行动，更契合现代意义的公共知识分子之定义，也就是所谓“公知”。</p>\n<p>而袁小靓曾以“打公知”知名并自豪。</p>\n<p>所谓“不打不相识”，普通境界的是成朋友，中等境界是成同事，最高境界，是结合为夫妻。</p>\n<p>袁小靓女士职场道路之右倾转弯，似乎对标了宋氏三姐妹之庆龄，也担负起了重任，达成了担当一位海外著名华领生活秘书之人生愿景。</p>\n<p>杨常年生活于海外，但与内地有千丝万缕的联系，也一度成为“大外宣”栋梁，参与为伟大时代鼓与呼的各种活动，娓娓道来厉害了我的国（注：中国）。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604553\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/29-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"592\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/29-1.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/29-1-253x300.jpg 253w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604555\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/30.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"578\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/30.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/30-260x300.jpg 260w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>正能量名人行，各种溢美背书，或正是这样的奔忙的旅途中，公知与“打公知”的袁小靓找到共鸣，也就是不分东南西北前后左右的最大公约数。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">▼▼▼</p>\n<p>月有阴晴圆缺，人有旦夕祸福。</p>\n<p>2019年1月18日杨先生在内地失联，疑被当局扣押。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604556\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/31.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"387\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/31.jpg 799w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/31-300x232.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/31-768x595.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>澳大利亚广播公司援引澳外交部消息称：中方已知会澳大利亚领事官员，杨在中国被扣查，澳方正了解被扣查原因，并寻求领事探视。</p>\n<p>2011年杨有过类似经历，也是友人放风被扣，事后杨解释道歉，失联因身体有恙并手机关机。</p>\n<p>杨的推特最后更新日期为2019年1月17日，朋友圈为18日，鄙人23日上午的私信，未获回复。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604560\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/32.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"771\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/32.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/32-195x300.jpg 195w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/32-664x1024.jpg 664w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n</div>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604561\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/33.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"439\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/33.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/33-300x263.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604562\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/34.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"1113\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/34.jpg 1050w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/34-135x300.jpg 135w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/34-768x1709.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/34-460x1024.jpg 460w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<div class=\"text_exposed_show\">\n<p>据BBC等媒体报道，与杨同行回国的，还有妻子袁瑞娟女士。</p>\n<p>在杨先生被扣三天之后的1月20日，袁女士发了一条抵达北京首都国际机场的微博。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604563\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/36.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"557\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/36.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/36-269x300.jpg 269w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/36-768x856.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/36-919x1024.jpg 919w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>袁小靓是袁瑞娟的笔名，她还曾代言过网红级ID：染香。</p>\n<p>坊间感慨：</p>\n<p>自纽约携眷归故国，疑谍影羊城被头套。</p>\n<p>2019年1月24日，大陆外交部正式发布消息，杨被拘捕一事，实锤了。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604564\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/37.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"731\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/37.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/37-205x300.jpg 205w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/37-768x1122.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/37-701x1024.jpg 701w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">▼▼▼</p>\n<p>话已至此，需要对“染香”这个著名ID做一个梳理澄清。</p>\n<p>染香一般指袁小靓，正能量公关女明星，海外右翼华领杨先生恒均生活秘书（后结为夫妻）；染香姐姐则是民间维权人士， 南方周末事件主角之一，辗转流亡，现居美国；媣稥则是前江苏公安厅干警李某江网名，后被销号，现用网名千钧客，最知名的大陆正能量斗士之一。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604565\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/38.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"651\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/38.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/38-230x300.jpg 230w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>媣稥，已被销号</em></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604566\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/39.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"696\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/39.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/39-216x300.jpg 216w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>鹰帝验明媣稥转世正身</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">▼▼▼</p>\n<p>君得小靓妇靠骄杨，这杰出华领与生活秘书的日常， 一度开始变得不那么恢弘壮大，风停雨歇，晾衣晒被，婆婆妈妈事，油盐酱醋茶。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604567\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/40.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"656\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/40.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/40-229x300.jpg 229w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>推友赞这一时佳话：老杨头巧施壮男计，粉红军痛失靓先锋。</p>\n<p>横批：左右逢源。</p>\n<p>又及：</p>\n<p>说鄙人此文为怼恒均先生，冤枉。</p>\n<p>有过一面之缘，彼时四十大几的老杨头，机敏跃动，倒像三十出头。</p>\n<p>娃言无忌，也时不时调侃他党员身份，揶揄其大一统情怀。</p>\n<p>尤其爱看他与南子等比党龄比贡献时的声情并茂。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604568\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/41.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"606\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/41.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/41-248x300.jpg 248w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/41-768x931.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/41-845x1024.jpg 845w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>一个自带charisma气质的趣人， 可算不伪不妄。</p>\n<p>算不得朋友。</p>\n<p>没友情包袱也好，可以表达喜欢，也可随性吐槽。</p>\n<p>是为记。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604569\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/42.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"25\" /></p>\n<p>END</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604570\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/43.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"376\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/43.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/43-300x226.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/43-768x577.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/43-1024x770.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n</div>\n<p>相关阅读：</p>\n<ul class=\"st-related-posts\">\n<li><span class=\"related_date\">2019.01.23</span> <a title=\"BBC | 杨恒均在华失踪：澳大利亚向中国寻求澳籍华裔作家下落\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/01/bbc-%e6%9d%a8%e6%81%92%e5%9d%87%e5%9c%a8%e5%8d%8e%e5%a4%b1%e8%b8%aa%ef%bc%9a%e6%be%b3%e5%a4%a7%e5%88%a9%e4%ba%9a%e5%90%91%e4%b8%ad%e5%9b%bd%e5%af%bb%e6%b1%82%e6%be%b3%e7%b1%8d%e5%8d%8e%e8%a3%94/\">BBC | 杨恒均在华失踪：澳大利亚向中国寻求澳籍华裔作家下落</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"related_date\">2018.05.24</span> <a title=\"【众人推】爱国大V染香移居美国，原来一切都是生意\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/05/%e3%80%90%e4%bc%97%e4%ba%ba%e6%8e%a8%e3%80%91%e7%88%b1%e5%9b%bd%e5%a4%a7v%e6%9f%93%e9%a6%99%e7%a7%bb%e5%b1%85%e7%be%8e%e5%9b%bd%ef%bc%8c%e5%8e%9f%e6%9d%a5%e4%b8%80%e5%88%87%e9%83%bd%e6%98%af%e7%94%9f/\">【众人推】爱国大V染香移居美国，原来一切都是生意</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"related_date\">2018.05.24</span> <a title=\"文三娃：染香故事\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/05/%e6%96%87%e4%b8%89%e5%a8%83%ef%bc%9a%e6%9f%93%e9%a6%99%e6%95%85%e4%ba%8b/\">文三娃：染香故事</a></li>\n</ul>\n","author":971,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,23855],"tags":[8635,19287,17288,37724,9909,34726,12039,8634,23678]}